item.description: PATRICK JASON MAYO of Stevens Point, WI died September 24, 2019 at the age of 46. During his funeral service career, he was employed at Bradley Funeral Home in Antigo, Gunderson Funeral Home in Madison, Peterson-Kramer Funeral Home in Wausau, and at the time of his passing Helke Funeral Home in Wausau.
